OL,3,CPair found guilty of murder after
OL,4,C'horrific' arson attack caught on CCTV
OL,6,FTwo men who launched a "horrific"
OL,7,Farson attack on a family home, killing
OL,8,Fa 26-year-old man and leaving his
OL,9,Fmother with life-changing injuries,
OL,10,Fhave both been found guilty of murder.
OL,12,FA three-week trial at Wolverhampton
OL,13,FCrown Court was told that a security
OL,14,Fcamera filmed Daniel Tatters as he
OL,15,Fsmashed and removed a bay window at
OL,16,Fthe home of Akashdeep Singh, before
OL,17,Fusing a flammable liquid to engulf the
OL,18,Fliving room in flames.
