OL,3,CPair found guilty of murder after
OL,4,C'horrific' arson attack caught on CCTV
OL,6,FMr Singh died in hospital hours later
OL,7,Fafter being trapped upstairs by the
OL,8,Fblaze at his home in Plascom Road,
OL,9,FEast Park, Wolverhampton, which the
OL,10,Fcourt heard may have been targeted by
OL,11,Fmistake.
OL,13,FTatters and Dale Francis, who acted as
OL,14,Fa driver and look-out at the scene,
OL,15,Fwere both unanimously convicted of
OL,16,Fmurder, arson with intent to endanger
OL,17,Flife and attempted murder on Tuesday
OL,18,Fafter jurors deliberated for more than
OL,19,Fnine hours.
