OL,3,CPair found guilty of murder after
OL,4,C'horrific' arson attack caught on CCTV
OL,6,FCCTV footage from the trial showed
OL,7,FTatters, who is from Stoke-on-Trent
OL,8,Fbut of no fixed address, approaching
OL,9,Fthe house carrying a container and
OL,10,Fhammering out the window before
OL,11,Frunning away as a fireball filled the
OL,12,Flounge.
OL,14,FProsecutors alleged that Tatters, 26,
OL,15,Fand 37-year-old Francis had started
OL,16,Fthe fire at about 1am on June 25 last
OL,17,Fyear "as the outcome of a considered
OL,18,Fagreement" following several previous
OL,19,Fjourneys to familiarise themselves
OL,20,Fwith the area.
