OL,6,FA lighter found by fire crews near the
OL,7,Fbay window was found to have Tatters's
OL,8,FDNA on it, while phone records, an in-
OL,9,Fcar tracking device and other CCTV
OL,10,Ffootage linked Francis, of Clare
OL,11,FStreet, Basford, Stoke-on-Trent, to
OL,12,Fthe attack.
OL,14,FTatters told jurors he had never been
OL,15,Fto Wolverhampton and had cut his hand
OL,16,Fon a glass pane while falling over in
OL,17,Fhis garden.
