OL,6,FFrancis, whose barrister described the
OL,7,Fconsequences of the fire as tragic and
OL,8,Fhorrific, declined to give evidence,
OL,9,Fclaiming in a written statement he
OL,10,Fthought his accomplice only intended
OL,11,Fto "torch" a car.
OL,13,FProsecutor Mark Heywood KC opened the
OL,14,Fcase at the start of the trial, saying
OL,15,Fthe defendants had travelled around 40
OL,16,Fmiles from Stoke-on-Trent in Francis's
OL,17,FVolkswagen Golf.
