OL,6,FTatters visited the Royal Stoke
OL,7,FUniversity Hospital around two-and-a-
OL,8,Fhalf hours after the fire for
OL,9,Ftreatment for cuts to his fingers.
OL,11,FCCTV proved Tatters, who was staying
OL,12,Fat an address in Sneyd Green, Stoke-on-
OL,13,FTrent, went on foot to Plascom Road
OL,14,Fafter the Golf was parked in
OL,15,FSutherland Avenue, around a third of a
OL,16,Fmile away.
