OL,6,FThe footage also showed the driver's
OL,7,Fdoor of the Golf being opened minutes
OL,8,Fbefore two figures were seen entering
OL,9,FEast Park at a location said to be a
OL,10,Fsix-minute walk to Plascom Road.
OL,12,F"Each of them shared the intention to
OL,13,Fmurder all the occupants"
OL,15,FMr Heywood told the court: "Their
OL,16,Factions make it clear that, whichever
OL,17,Fone of them actually started the fire,
OL,18,Feach of them shared the intention to
OL,19,Fmurder all the occupants and each
OL,20,Fassisted and/or encouraged the other
OL,21,Fto carry that out as planned.
